## Payrails Demo Environment Variables (.env.example)
# Copy to `.env.local` then fill in real values.
# NEVER commit real secrets. NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars are safe for client exposure; others are server-only.

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Required (Server-side OAuth)
PAYRAILS_CLIENT_ID="your_client_id_here"
PAYRAILS_CLIENT_SECRET="your_client_secret_here"  # server-only secret
PAYRAILS_BASE_URL="https://demo-api.staging.payrails.io"

# Workspace ID (non-secret)
PAYRAILS_WORKSPACE_ID="your_workspace_id_here"

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Suggested future vars (uncomment as needed):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYRAILS_REDIRECT_SUCCESS="/order/success"
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYRAILS_REDIRECT_FAILURE="/order/failure"
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYRAILS_REDIRECT_ERROR="/order/failure?reason=error"

# After editing env values restart the dev server.

